&lt;p&gt;Data is core to our growing business and has been ingrained in the company&#39;s DNA since its founding. As a member of the Data Analytics team, you will partner closely with Product, Engineering, and other business stakeholders to identify opportunities where machine learning, AI, and advanced analytics can create meaningful customer and business value.&lt;/p&gt;
