&lt;li&gt;Assist in preparation of materials for Board of Director meetings&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work on a variety of special projects that may include M&amp;amp;A, financings, new business initiatives, etc.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
