&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have a bachelor&#39;s Degree in Business, Finance, Accounting or Statistics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2-3 years experience of finance and/or strategic analysis experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have entrepreneurial drive, excellent communication and interpersonal skills with demonstrated ability to work in a fast paced and dynamic environment&lt;/li&gt;
